#: app/templates/admin/index.html:43
msgid "⚠️ Admin Tips"
msgstr "⚠️ Leideanna Riaracháin"

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:45
msgid ""
"Never run in production with DEBUG enabled. Debug mode exposes internal "
"details and stack traces."
msgstr ""
"Nka nnyɛ edwuma wɔ abɔɛ mu a wɔde DEBUG renyim. Debug tumi yɛ adwuma a ɛma "
"wɔhwɛ ɔman nsɛm ne nhoma mpɔtam anaa ɛyɛ a wɔyɛ yɛn mpɔtam."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:47
msgid ""
"Always deploy Grylli behind a reverse proxy (e.g. Caddy, Nginx, or Traefik) "
"and serve it over HTTPS. Sensitive user data must be encrypted in transit."
msgstr ""
"Momma Gyia Grylli wɔ w'akyi ɔbrɛwenniɛ ɛyɛ Caddy, Nginx sɛnea wɔyɛ no "
"ɔkyikwan so, na sɛnea wɔde yɛka ɔkɛsee ɛyɛ HTTPS. Nsɛm a ɛyɛ den ama ɔman "
"foforɔ ɛsɛ sɛ ɔyɛ nsɛm a wɔde bɔhɔsɛm di akɔmu."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:50
msgid ""
"Ensure the data folder (database) is backed up regularly. Backups are stored"
" in the 'backups' folder."
msgstr ""
"Déan cinnte go bhfuil fillteán sonraí (bunachar sonraí) tacaíocht suas ar do"
" óstach."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:53
msgid ""
"The uploads folder is shared. To isolate attachments per user, configure "
"host-level directories and access controls."
msgstr ""
"Tá an fillteán uaslódálacha roinnte. Chun iatáin a leithlisiú de réir "
"úsáideora, cumraigh eolaire leibhéal an fhreastalaí agus rialuithe rochtana."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:55
msgid ""
"To restore a backup: stop the container, replace the grylli.db file from a "
"backup, and restart."
msgstr ""
"Chun cóip chúltaca a athbhunú: stad an coimeádán, cuir an data/grylli.db in "
"ionad ceann ón bhfillteán cúltacaí, agus atosú an coimeádán."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:56
msgid ""
"Admins cannot remove their own admin role to prevent accidental lockout."
msgstr ""
"Ní féidir le riarthóirí a ról riarthóra féin a bhaint chun cosc a chur ar "
"ghlasáil dhe thimpiste."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:58
msgid ""
"Rate limits and automatic account lockouts are enforced to protect against "
"brute-force login attempts."
msgstr ""
"Ráta teorainneacha agus glasáil cuntas uathoibríoch á gcur i bhfeidhm chun "
"cosaint a dhéanamh i gcoinne iarrachtaí logála isteach fórsa brúidiúil."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:60
msgid ""
"Passwords, SMTP credentials, and API tokens are encrypted at rest using "
"Fernet."
msgstr ""
"Pasfhocail, dintiúir SMTP, agus comharthaí API criptéite i suaimhneas ag "
"úsáid Fernet."

